# CI evaluation artifacts — ignore everything except the tracked baseline.
# Using `ci_results/*` (not `ci_results/`) so the negation below can
# re-include baseline.json; a trailing-slash dir ignore would prevent that.
ci_results/*
!ci_results/baseline.json